{"tid":2005202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧押後提交香港報告","createTime":"2020-05-07T03:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T00:55:14.000Z","uid":241764,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bfcc85e9735bf6fe16bec6de4a4856009629db91","tid":2005202,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧當地時間周三（6日）在記者會表示，國務院會押後向國會提交有關香港的報告。他稱，考慮到北京本月22日舉行全國人民代表大會會議，關注會否有進一步削弱香港自治的行動。他沒提及報告預計提交日期。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普去年簽署《香港人權與民主法案》，國務院原定5月底提交報告，評估香港的高度自治有否受到侵蝕，以及潛在侵蝕對美港合作的影響，標示華府應否維持對港特殊待遇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200507/s00001/1588810959400/%e8%93%ac%e4%bd%a9%e5%a5%a7%e6%8a%bc%e5%be%8c%e6%8f%90%e4%ba%a4%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%a0%b1%e5%91%8a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200507%2Fs00001%2F1588810959400%2F%25e8%2593%25ac%25e4%25bd%25a9%25e5%25a5%25a7%25e6%258a%25bc%25e5%25be%258c%25e6%258f%2590%25e4%25ba%25a4%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25a0%25b1%25e5%2591%258a&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdQmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=509ec1b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200507%2Fs00001%2F1588810959400%2F%25e8%2593%25ac%25e4%25bd%25a9%25e5%25a5%25a7%25e6%258a%25bc%25e5%25be%258c%25e6%258f%2590%25e4%25ba%25a4%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25a0%25b1%25e5%2591%258a&h=15706f64\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200507/s00001/1588810959400/%e8%93%ac%e4%bd%a9%e5%a5%a7%e6%8a%bc%e5%be%8c%e6%8f%90%e4%ba%a4%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%a0%b1%e5%91%8a</a>"},{"pid":"6f4ceb32855f779ca950c4a8c24ad9a190842a60","tid":2005202,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:20:17.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkg